EN: Asset management is a complex field that requires expertise and experience.

ZH: 我们需要对公司的资产进行定期评估，以确定价值和风险。
EN: We need to conduct regular evaluations of the company's assets to determine value and risk.

ZH: 这项交易将极大地增加我们的资产负债表。
EN: This deal will greatly increase our asset balance sheet.

ZH: 每位继承人都有权分享遗产中的资产。
EN: Each heir has the right to share the assets in the inheritance.

ZH: 养老金是一种重要的养老金资产。
EN: Pension is an important retirement asset.

ZH: 艺术品也可以是一种有价值的资产，可以增值。
EN: Artwork can also be a valuable asset that appreciates in value.

